CBRE is pleased to offer 1,000-3,000sqm* of functional warehouse space available for lease. Direct access to Victoria Street & in close proximity to the M4 & M7 Motorways.

Features Include:

+ Internal clearance of between 7m - 8.5m*
+ Large concrete manoeuvring area
+ Expansive awning for all weather loading/unloading
+ Fully racked facility which can be partially removed
+ Would suit a range of different users in need of overflow storage
+ Available Now
 
Please contact the exclusive agent for further information.
